<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sign-v">sign <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /saɪn/    美 /saɪn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>签 (名)；签字 (于信、文件等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>sign an agreement</strong> / <strong>a contract</strong>
签协议/合同</p></div>

<h4 id="2-signal">2.<strong>示意；以手势表示 (signal)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The teacher signed me to enter.
老师打手势示意我进来。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="sign-up-for">sign up (for)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>报名参加 (课程等)；登记注册：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>sign up for the course in advance
提前报名参加课程</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m ready to sign up for the mid July group.
我准备报名参加7月中旬的那个团。</p></div></div>